The Gaudi Pool II is the ideal apartment for study abroad students in Barcelona. It can accommodate up to 6 people with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a living room and a complete kitchen. Other apartment features include: elevator access, A/C, a hairdryer, an iron, a washing machine, a TV and Internet. It also has a balcony and a swimming pool so after long days of classes or traveling you can relax in the sun!

