The Sant Pere apartment complex is located in the center of Barcelona with just a five- minute walk to areas like Plaza Catalunya &amp; Las Ramblas and just 20 feet away from the metro station and bus stop. This close proximity to the center of the city and to travel aids makes the Sant Pere apartment complex an excellent choice for study abroad students.

The apartment can comfortably sleep up to 12 individuals, which makes it easy for large groups of friends to live together while abroad. There are five bedrooms, two ½ baths, a living room with high ceilings and a fully equipped kitchen.

