This spacious and bright Florence apartment is just steps away
from Ponte Vecchio, Uffizi Gallery and Piazza Santa Croce. It is
located in a small piazza facing a pretty internal courtyard, and
is surrounded by shops, a super market, and tons of restaurants. This tranquil and private location is ideal for living abroad. This apartment can sleep up to 8 and is located on the third floor without an elevator). The lounge area is large and luminous, and overlooks the courtyard. It’s furnished with a sofa, TV and a dining area as well. There are 3 bedrooms, 2 of which have queen size beds and the last has a single bed. All three have plenty of storage space available. There are also 2 bathrooms, one includes a bathtub/shower, and the other has a walk in shower. The apartment also includes a fully equipped kitchen and laundry facilities. The Apartmentsflorence.it staff is always present to ensure consistency and high quality with their cleaning service, and whatever other assistance/ maintenance may be needed over the time of your stay.

&nbsp;

Located a small distance from the metro station, Plaza Catalunya and La Boqueria, as well as many other destinations, this apartment has much to offer to international study abroad students.

The Ramblas Boqueria apartment complex is recently renovated and refurnished with elevator access and 24-hour surveillance cameras. It can comfortably sleep 3 people with two bedrooms and one bathroom. Additional features include a plasma TV, Internet, A/C, heating, bed linens and towels, a washing machine with a dryer, a dishwasher, and a kitchen with all modern appliances.

&nbsp;

