The Ramblas Boqueria apartment complex is recently renovated and refurnished with elevator access and 24-hour surveillance cameras. It can comfortably sleep 6 people with four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and additional features of a plasma TV, Internet, A/C, heating, bed linen and towels, a washing machine with a dryer, a dishwasher and a kitchen with all modern appliances.

&nbsp;

The Arc de Teatre sits in heart of the Old City, just steps away from Las Ramblas. It is the perfect housing option for students looking to study abroad, located minutes from the La Boqueria supermarket, the Columbus monument, Montjuic Mountain, Old Port and Barceloneta, just to name a few. Students who have a passion for fashion can also find themselves a short distance from great shopping areas like Plaza Catalunya, Paseo de Gracia and Rambla de Catalunya. This apartment is ideal for international students’ looking to experience all Barcelona has to offer!

The apartment can house up to 4 international students with two bedrooms and one bathroom. It also features a living room, a dining room and a newly refurbished kitchen. Students can also enjoy the apartments TV, Internet, A/C, heating and a balcony during their stay.

&nbsp;

This beautiful apartment, located in Eixample, has various connections to all the must-see sites and attractions Barcelona has to offer. Being that it is about a five-minute walk from most international universities, it is ideal for students who are studying abroad. It’s also located in close proximity to the world- famous church Sagrada Familia which is a must-see historic site for everyone visiting the area.

The apartment is perfect for bigger groups- having enough space to comfortably sleep 6 people with four bedrooms and two bathrooms. It includes amenities such as a plasma TV, Internet, elevator access, A/C and heating, towels and bed linen, a washing machine and a dryer. It also comes with a furnished kitchen inclusive of a dishwasher, a microwave, an oven and cooking/ serving utensils.

&nbsp;

This study abroad apartment is in the perfect location. On via Ghibelina, you are walking distance from all of Florence’s historic landmarks, and surrounded by restaurants, shops and markets. Completely renovated in 2013, the apartment is bright and spacious. The apartment can accommodate up to 3 people comfortably for long stays as it consists of 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a spacious living room with a full-size sofa bed. The master bedroom has a queen bed, and the second has two single beds and overlooks a delightful balcony. The kitchen is fully equipped complete with all the necessities. The apartment also has a wonderful balcony.

