In prime central Florence location right near the Duomo, this is a great rental option for international students.

1 bedroom apartment located on the second floor of an elegant Florentine style apartment on Via delle Belle Donne. It is located surrounded by nice cafes and shops, and only a 300-meter walk to the Duomo. An ideal starting point for exploring all that the city has to offer.

The apartment can accommodate up to 3 people comfortably with 1 bedroom on the first floor and a room on the mezzanine level, 2 bathrooms and laundry facilities.

The living room is complete with a sofa bed for guests and there is a small outdoor balcony, which overlooks an internal courtyard of the building. The first bedroom has a large queen sized bed and there is a small staircase in the living room that leads to a mezzanine level that feature 2 single beds. This mezzanine level is not standing height (1.60 mt - 62.99 inches)

